INSERT INTO `course` (`ID`,`school`,`major`,`number`,`units`,`name`,`description`,`semester`) VALUES (658,'Dornsife','IR','381',4,'Introduction to International Security','Key concepts in international security studies; historical evolution of international warfare and diplomacy; contemporary international security issues.',1);
INSERT INTO `course` (`ID`,`school`,`major`,`number`,`units`,`name`,`description`,`semester`) VALUES (659,'Dornsife','IR','385',4,'European Foreign Policy and Security Issues','In-depth analysis of foreign policy events and cases in Europe in the 20th century; focus on security issues.',1);
INSERT INTO `course` (`ID`,`school`,`major`,`number`,`units`,`name`,`description`,`semester`) VALUES (660,'Dornsife','IR','386',4,'Terrorism and Counterterrorism','Examination of terrorism and responses to terrorism, including how societies understand and deal with terrorism; focus on ethical and normative issues.',1);
