INSERT INTO `course` (`ID`,`school`,`major`,`number`,`units`,`name`,`description`,`semester`) VALUES (2608,'Viterbi','CSCI','670',4,'Advanced Analysis of Algorithms','Fundamental techniques for design and analysis of algorithms. Dynamic programming; network flows; theory of NP-completeness; linear programming; approximation, randomized, and online algorithms; basic cryptography. Prerequisite: CSCI 570. <strong>Recommended preparation:</strong> familiarity with algorithms and discrete mathematics. Open only to doctoral students.',1);
INSERT INTO `course` (`ID`,`school`,`major`,`number`,`units`,`name`,`description`,`semester`) VALUES (2609,'Viterbi','CSCI','671',4,'Randomized Algorithms','Standard techniques in the design and analysis of randomized algorithms and random structures. Topics include tail bounds, Markov Chains, VC-dimension, probabilistic method. Prerequisite: CSCI 570 or CSCI 670. <strong>Recommended preparation:</strong> Basic background in probability and linear algebra.',1);
INSERT INTO `course` (`ID`,`school`,`major`,`number`,`units`,`name`,`description`,`semester`) VALUES (2610,'Viterbi','CSCI','677',4,'Advanced Computer Vision','Fundamental issues in computer vision: theory, algorithms and applications. Image formation, image segmentation, inference and measurement of 3-D, motion analysis, object and activity recognition.',1);
