INSERT INTO `course` (`ID`,`school`,`major`,`number`,`units`,`name`,`description`,`semester`) VALUES (3297,'Keck','PCPA','509',4,'Behavioral Sciences III','In a seminar format, information management and research methods are explored as well as ethical issues of PA practice will be discussed. Open to Physician Assistant Practice majors only.',1);
INSERT INTO `course` (`ID`,`school`,`major`,`number`,`units`,`name`,`description`,`semester`) VALUES (3298,'Keck','PCPA','523',4,'Clinical Skills I','Laboratory experiences with basic clinical skills essential to medical practice. First of four courses. Open to Physician Assistant Practice majors only.',1);
INSERT INTO `course` (`ID`,`school`,`major`,`number`,`units`,`name`,`description`,`semester`) VALUES (3299,'Keck','PCPA','529',6,'Clinical Skills III','Laboratory experiences with basic clinical skills essential to medical practice. Third of four courses. Open to Physician Assistant Practice majors only.',1);
INSERT INTO `course` (`ID`,`school`,`major`,`number`,`units`,`name`,`description`,`semester`) VALUES (3300,'Keck','PCPA','530',6,'Basic Medical Sciences','A one semester overview of clinical anatomy, physiology, pathophysiology, and pathology essential to understanding disease mechanisms commonly encountered in primary care and specialty practices of medicine. Open to physician assistant practice majors only.',1);
INSERT INTO `course` (`ID`,`school`,`major`,`number`,`units`,`name`,`description`,`semester`) VALUES (3301,'Keck','PCPA','543',4,'Topics in Medicine I','Basic instruction in normal/abnormal states of organ systems in the study of disease. The first of three courses that includes instruction in pathophysiology, pharmacology, diagnostic studies, and medicine. Open to Physician Assistant Practice majors only.',1);
INSERT INTO `course` (`ID`,`school`,`major`,`number`,`units`,`name`,`description`,`semester`) VALUES (3302,'Keck','PCPA','549',6,'Topics in Medicine III','Basic instruction in normal/abnormal states of organ systems in the study of human disease. The third of three courses that includes instruction in pathophysiology, pharmacology, diagnostic studies, and medicine. Open to Physician Assistant Practice majors only.',1);
INSERT INTO `course` (`ID`,`school`,`major`,`number`,`units`,`name`,`description`,`semester`) VALUES (3303,'Keck','PCPA','563',3.5,'Clinical Assignment III','One discrete consecutive six-week long, five-day-a-week intensive field placement under a program approved supervising preceptor in a program-approved clinical setting. Requires departmental approval. Graded CR/NC.',1);
INSERT INTO `course` (`ID`,`school`,`major`,`number`,`units`,`name`,`description`,`semester`) VALUES (3304,'Keck','PCPA','566',3.5,'Clinical Assignment VI','One discrete consecutive six-week long, five-day-a-week intensive field placement under a program approved supervising preceptor in a program-appoved clinical setting. Requires departmental approval. Graded CR/NC.',1);
INSERT INTO `course` (`ID`,`school`,`major`,`number`,`units`,`name`,`description`,`semester`) VALUES (3305,'Keck','PCPA','567',3.5,'Clinical Assignment VII','One discrete consecutive six-week long, five-day-a-week intensive field placement under a program approved supervising preceptor in a program-approved clinical setting. Requires departmental approval. Graded CR/NC.',1);
